symptoms. There are great limitations to their performing daily chores, 
especially for heart-affected carriers. The support of the health team, 
especially the nurse's, is valuable to the clinical management of the patient. 
When it is started in the early stages of the disease, a better quality of life 
and a longer life expectancy can be reached.

